snippet.title: Miley Cyrus Bangerz Tour Controversy! (EXPLICIT VIDEO)

localized.description:
Miley Cyrus Bangerz Tour Controversy! (EXPLICIT VIDEO)
Subscribe to Hollywire | http://bit.ly/Sub2HotMinute
Send Chelsea a Tweet! | http://bit.ly/TweetChelsea
Follow Hollywire! | http://bit.ly/TweetHollywire

Miley Cyrus' Bangerz tour kicked off... well, with a bang. Flying hot dogs, giant tongues and dancing teddy bears. Yea, it was crazy

Miley kicked off the Bangerz extravaganza in Vancouver this weekend and proved that she is truly the current queen of shock. Here are just 5 of the craziest moments from the show. 

First off, it opened up with a giant picture of Miley —and when giant Miley's mouth opened up, a tongue slide rolled out — and the real Miley slid down it. Yes, that really happened. And yes, it might give you nightmares.

And then there was the moment where Miley straddled a giant flying hot dog. You heard me.

And of course it's not a Miley Cyrus concert without high-cut leotards. Her concert outfits were designed by the likes of Roberto Cavalli, Jeremy Scott, the Blonds and Marc Jacobs. And each was a work of gasp-worthy art.

The moment that had gotten pretty much everyone talking was when Miley pulled a Monica Lewinsky on a man dressed as Bill Clinton. 

And finally, Miley sang Adore You on top of a car and, well, it got intense.

Alright, I gotta know, what was your favorite part of the Bangerz tour you've seen? And are you seeing her in concert? Tell me all about it in the comments section below...
